  <name>AQtion</name>
  <summary>Fast-paced FPS multiplayer action game</summary>

  <description>
    <p>AQtion is the fully packaged ready-to-play version of Action Quake 2</p>
    <p>Features include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>realistic weaponry and gunplay, locational damage</li>
      <li>deathmatch, teamplay, team deathmatch, CTF and other modes available</li>
      <li>offline and online bots available to practice your skills</li>
      <li>hundreds of maps and servers all over the world</li>
      <li>main client based on the popuar Q2Pro (http://skuller.net/q2pro)</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

